<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.4">
<l>mayarvaṟa veṉmaṉattē maṉṉiṉāṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>yuyarviṉai yētaru moṇcuṭark kaṟṟaiyai</l>
<l>yayarvi lamararka ḷātik koḻuntaiyeṉ</l>
<l>ṉicaiviṉai yeṉcolli yāṉviṭuvēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Him who remains in my mind so that confusion is cut off,</l>
<l>the bundle of bright light that brings elevation,</l>
<l>the tireless primary sprout of the immortals,</l>
<l>my contentment – saying what shall I give [him] up?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
